These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, may, january
House: townhouse, art-deco, wooden, modern
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, basketball, ice-hockey
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, taxi, tram
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person driving the tram##2
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person driving the car is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Birthday           | may | june   | january | september |
| House   | townhouse      | art-deco | wooden              | modern |
| Sport   | water-polo       | biathlon     | ice-hockey               | basketball    |
| Beverage           | water        | 7up     | hot-chocolate           | almond-milk       |
| Transport     | helicopter | taxi     | car                | tram      |

