.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
City: berlin, rome, edinburgh, prague
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, romeade, iced-tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, dannemann, ritmeester
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, mah-jongg, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person drinking romeade is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the person drinking juice is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person playing bridge##2
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking romeade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking romeade##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking romeade is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking romeade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| City          | edinburgh       | rome      | berlin      | prague      |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | juice | romeade | tea |
| Cigar   | ritmeester          | bongani       | dannemann            | game      |
| Game           | poker            | mah-jongg    | bridge           | canasta       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

