The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, taxi, skateboard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, davidoff, chaman, dannemann
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the social-worker##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the freelancer##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person driving the trike is the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is between the analyst and the vegafina-smoker##2
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
11. the person watching action movies is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | asparagus  | strawberry | grapefruit |
| Job   | social-worker   | freelancer        | analyst | software-developer     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | animation    | epic  | martial-arts   |
| Transport           | taxi     | skateboard      | trike | motorbike        |
| Cigar         | vegafina      | dannemann | davidoff      | chaman     |

