.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, december, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, jazz, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, argentine, canadian, australian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, daffodil, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is between the fan of disco and the fan of house##2
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the polish##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is the polish##1
 5. the fan of house is between the polish and the person who growsbellflower##2
 6. the australian is on the far left##1
 7. the argentine is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who growsamaryllis and the fan of jazz##2
10. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday      | june     | november | december    | february          |
| Movie-Genre          | western | satire     | time-travel | adventure         |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | house       | pop         | disco        |
| Nationality         | australian  | argentine     | polish     | canadian |
| Flower     | bellflower     | daffodil      | amaryllis   | balloon-flower          |

