The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, indie, r&b, country
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game, cain, siglo
 1. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the fan of country is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person driving the van##2
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Game          | bridge    | mah-jongg        | poker    | whist   |
