.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, banana, lemon, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, may, november
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, scrabble, mah-jongg
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, car, train
City: san-francisco, venice, liverpool, hamburg
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person driving the train is the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing scrabble and the person eating avocado##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person eating avocado and the person who's birthday is in may##2
11. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food          | avocado       | lemon       | pomegranate | banana    |
| Birthday         | march     | november | may | april     |
| Game           | canasta        | mah-jongg    | scrabble  | backgammon |
| Transport   | skateboard      | car      | train     | helicopter     |
| City         | hamburg | liverpool      | venice    | san-francisco |

