 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person eating carrot##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
11. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |    4     |
