 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's birthday is in zombieing##1
11. the person who's birthday is in zombieing is between the davidoff-smoker and the person watching comedy movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person watching horror movies and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Flower      | tulip      | balloon-flower         | rose | orchid      |
| Cigar           | davidoff | prince | vegafina | pall-mall     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | indie          | ambient  | electronic |
| Birthday         | january        | zombieing  | august | september   |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie    | adventure         | comedy     | horror     |

