 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 3. the futuristic house is the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 5. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the futuristic house is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of gospel##1
 8. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the fan of trance##1
10. the modern house is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is between the fan of gospel and the victorian house##2

