.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, snooker, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, family, musical, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, pakistani, thai
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, milk, fanta
House: art-deco, modern, tower, craftsman
 1. the person watching superhero movies is the malaysian##1
 2. the craftsman house is between the thai and the person drinking tea##2
 3. the modern house is between the person drinking lemonade and the tower house##2
 4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the modern house is on the left of the tower house##1
10. the person playing chess is the japanese##1
11. the japanese is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Game         | snooker  | go | monopoly | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | family   | musical      | action    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani | thai        | japanese     |
| Beverage         | tea  | lemonade  | milk     | fanta      |
| House     | art-deco | craftsman      | modern   | tower       |

 